# Cloud Front
    Content Delivery Network CDN
        Improves read performance, content is cached at the edge
        216 Points of Presence globally
        DDos Protection (because www), integration with Shield and AWS WAF
        Great for static content that must be available everywhere

# S3 Cross Region Replication
    Must be setup for each region 
    Files area updated in near real-time
    Read Only
    Great for dynamin content that needs to be available at low-latency in few regions

# Cloud Front - Origins
    S3 bucket
        Distributing files and caching
        Security with Cloud Front Origin Access Control (OAC)
        Can be used as an ingress to upload files to S3

    Custom Origin HTTP
        ALB
        EC2
        S3 website
        Any HTTP backend

# CloudFront Geo Restriction
    Can restrict who can access your distribution
        Allowlist: Allow your users to access content, countries on a list approved

        Blocklist: Prevent users from accessing content, countries on a list of banned

# Cache Invalidations
    In case update backend origin, Cloudfront doesn't know about
    Force an entire or parcial cache refrest
    Invalidate all files (*) or special path (/images/*)

# Global Accelerator
    Unicast IP - one server hold IP
    Anycast - all servers hold the same IP

    Global accelerator is Anycast, 2 IP, send traffic directly to Edge Locations
    The Edge Location send the traffic to application
    Works with EC2, Elastic IP, ALB, NBL, public or private

    Performance
        Intelligent routing to lowest latency and fast regional failover
        No issue with client cache (because the IP doesn't change)
        Internal AWS network

    Health Check
        Performs health check of applications
        Help make application global (failover less than 1 minute for unhealthy)
        Great for DR

    Security
        only 2 IP need to be whitlist
        DDos

# Global Accelerator â‰  CloudFront
    Both use the AWS Global network and edge location around the world
    Services integrate with AWS Shield DDos

    CloudFront
        Improves performance cache content (images and videos)
        Dynamic content
    
    Global Accelerator
        Performance for wide range of applications over TCP or UDP
        Proxying packets at the edge to applications
        Good for no-HTTP/HTTP, as gaming (UDP), IoT (MQTT) or Voice IP and static IP.


        
    
